  "shortDescription": "Display multiple hearts in different state based on health",
  "version": "",
  "description": [
    "Useful for displaying health as images with different states.",
    "For example hearts (heart pie) which have different fill animations based on your health",
    "Clones will be created if you change animation or health or clones count",
    "This action should run every frame",
    "",
    "Import all your images as single animation and use one action to control it.",
    "Tips are in action description in events sheet.",
    "Stay healthly <3"
  ],
